00:03:19.965 --> 00:03:27.673
but also he talked of the resurrection time

00:03:27.965 --> 00:03:30.257
when your hands will speak.

00:03:30.590 --> 00:03:32.882
Two things He said,

00:03:33.090 --> 00:03:35.590
first that your hands will speak

00:03:35.882 --> 00:03:39.090
when you will get your realisation .

00:03:39.381 --> 00:03:43.673
