00:06:56.299 --> 00:06:59.798
they found flowers, two types of flower one for Hindus

00:07:00.132 --> 00:07:04.715
and one for Muslims,

00:07:05.007 --> 00:07:07.132
so that's how he have solved the problems

00:07:07.299 --> 00:07:10.299
